published on 2022-12-19T05:44:58Z

Here' my recreation of John Addison's theme music from "Murder, She Wrote" in remembrance of Dame Angela Lansbury, who passed away peacefull on October 11th. Enjoy! All musical material is pre-recorded using virtually-sampled instruments and does not use, in any form, the original music or any feature of the original recording.
